      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FIREBALL ZED (2) boasts a strong record this journey here with two wins and three minors from six tries. Was out of the placings last time (23.46) at The Gardens in a Grade 4/5, finishing sixth and beaten 10 lengths. Appeals as a leading chance in this. BEAR'S HEAD (8) has missed the placings at his last couple but was in the money three back when second (30.12) at The Gardens in a Grade 5. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can improve sharply here. SLEEK APOLLO (1) looks close to win after hitting the frame last run (19.94) at Bulli in a Grade 5. Has first look at box 1 this time. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Leading chance. MAKE YOUR STAND (3) is a last-start placegetter in a fast-run race - should be thereabouts.",
